-afk-2.25-hours-still-burn-pops-burn-someone-score-fungi-playerauction-rinse,repeat*<br><br>2. Disable Manaburn altogether in pvp - ANY wizard with both critical nuke3 and the class +% nuke skill can tell you that they crit a HEAP. Sunstrike - 3260 dmg ? Like that isnt bad enough that they need to include a death touch... And yes they also need to fix the pvp damage of critical nukes, it IS still broken which is rather ridiculous.<br><br>3. Dramatically change the skill all together. some alternatives ?<br>a) Inner Peace - an instant cast harvest type skill that increases mana much like the harvest spell does - with a relatively small recycle time, much like the mend skill for monks. 10 mins sounds about fair on recycle.. maybe 450 mana?<br>b) Spell Evasion - Acts as a &quot;hate-controller&quot;, with a 1min 30 seconds recycle, the next spell cast will result in no addition to your agro. Or alternatively this could have a permanent percentage of &quot;hate-reduction&quot; - 3,5 and 10% doesnt sound unfair.<br>c) Spellburn - with a 72 minture recycle time, the next spell cast will be absolutely free of mana cost and instant casting.<br><br><br>k well its late and I cant think of any more alternatives. Thoughts ? flames ? alternatives ? Feel free.<br> <p>Neckros Dundee"That's not a knife..."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uwootling.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Woot Ling</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#333333>(3/13/02 5:22:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=625.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://users.bigpond.net.au/woot/images/woot4.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: We all want it nerfed - but what are alternatives ?</span><hr size=1> Man